00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:24,000
Good morning!

833
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:30,000
This reminded me to tell you that it's time to head to the fishing hole!

834
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:32,000
Hey!

835
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:36,000
Whatever became of your remind-a-tronic thing, huh?

836
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:38,000
Trust me on this one!

837
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:42,000
We're better off forgetting all about that silly thing!

838
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:46,000
But those reminder-naughts of yours really are a clever idea!

839
00:34:46,000 --> 00:34:47,000
Know what, Bucky?

840
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,000
What?

841
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:50,000
The most important reminders aren't here, you see!

842
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:52,000
They're down here!

843
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:56,000
Well, I'll certainly never forget my best friend!

844
00:34:56,000 --> 00:35:02,000
So, have those reminder-naughts ever woken you up in the middle of the night?

845
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,000
We'll see you next time!

846
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:06,000
Bye!

847
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,000
We'll see you next time!

848
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,000
Bye!

849
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:12,000
Bye!

